description: Diva Duck Food Truck is bringing divine comfort cuisine to Bakersfield. You’ll find a fine variety of candy, snacks, and cool beverages on one side. On the other, you’ll discover a delectable selection of dazzling daily specials, like Biscuits & Gravy, Chorizo & Egg Burritos, or Southwestern Steak Salad.Once you waddle on over to this truck, you too will surely declare: “Viva Diva Duck!”
name: Diva Duck Food Truck
